.title Help: Audio Package
ABOUT THIS PACKAGE
The Audio package provides support for audio.  It includes
hardware drivers for soundcards, a SCO Admin Audio Configuration
Manager, and basic audio utilities.

EXITING THE PACKAGE SELECTION MENU
Press <Enter> to enter your selections and to return to the
Install Menu.

EXITING HELP
Press <Esc> to return to the Package Selection menu.
Press <F1> for more help.
